Input:
```mlir
firrtl.circuit "InstanceSym" {
  firrtl.extmodule @Foo(out x : !firrtl.bundle<a: uint<1>>)
  firrtl.module @InstanceSym() {
    firrtl.instance foo sym @foo @Foo(out x : !firrtl.bundle<a: uint<1>> sym [<@b_0,1,public>])
  }
}
```

InstanceOp's don't support port symbols, should reject if the parsed port list (via helper) encounters symbols.
